{"tid":1829023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"維園年宵周日開幕　食環署安排全場緊急疏散演習","createTime":"2020-01-18T11:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T11:29:40.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7962511529558cb19eaa4796eeb64f5d55f1d4e7","tid":1829023,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:11:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3876631/org/b2d902dac70a28f4d5ceaafe5e010f88.jpg/YxvFBvroOsAkLIEXXn6eNQvq0sYFQShUNAYt3h4GLd4?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3876631%2Forg%2Fb2d902dac70a28f4d5ceaafe5e010f88.jpg%2FYxvFBvroOsAkLIEXXn6eNQvq0sYFQShUNAYt3h4GLd4%3Fv%3Dw480&h=edd21adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食環署人員今日下午3時許，透過場內廣播公布：「維園場內將於下午4時進行疏散演習，所有檔主檔員需即時停止手上工作，跟隨職員盡快離開現場，多謝合作」。其後有手持紅色反光棒的食環署人員，到各個攤檔講解相關指示，及帶領他們到出口等候，「佢淨係係咁叫我地哋快啲走，之後就叫我哋企喺廁所門口等」，歷時約15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n緊急疏散演習並非首次，售賣蘭花的曾小姐表示，昨日食環署曾經進行大規模疏散演習，模擬場內有人進行示威行動時，由食環署職員以反光棒，指示他們如何離開現場。她指這是擺檔多年來首次，「其實我哋都冇見過有人會你做啲乜嘢，聽日的確係有示威行動，但係唔會覺得會來到現場，同埋明白到佢哋都唔會係想影響到其他人。」她慨嘆今年因為社會氣氛，以及場內將會沒有任何乾貨攤位，人流減少最少一半，擔心不能回本離場。<br />\n<br />\n有經營花店10多年的檔主表示演習為多年來首次，感到有點愕然，雖然明白食環署的做法，「有啲過分擔心，唔講以為打緊仗。」"},{"pid":"16879289b0723ba984b6495a9b84025c97980a5b","tid":1829023,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:13:16.000Z","msg":"遊行完行年宵都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e064d3098f7204a30430b58774916ffca2fbf6","tid":1829023,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXADpiW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXADpiW.jpg&h=e0ea6049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.19遮打集會 早啲到<br />\n1.22荔枝角收押所<br />\n1.24荔枝角收押所<br />\n1.27和你shop</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O8J9pnD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO8J9pnD.jpg&h=59a5f02c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyA7Vuq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyA7Vuq.jpg&h=3f02ab45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSBSm9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSBSm9r.jpg&h=fac8cfa1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HMKXHM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HMKXHM.png&h=a3a1e633&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OaZD19s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOaZD19s.jpg&h=065725f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多聲援出庭手足</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVq0v20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVq0v20.jpg&h=524f4eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加入工會<br />\ntg: hkonstrike<br />\nFB: 二百萬三罷聯合戰線<br />\n‼️連儂廁<br />\n‼️Twitter戰線"}]}